Body: Description: Your appliance is running low on disk space, there is 6.7 gb free available from 19.52 gb (34%). EPP Server functionality and performance may be severely affected. Use Audit Log Backup to reduce the logs stored in the database, delete older system and audit log backups, and tune policies to reduce incoming log count. For further assistance contact Support.

What We've Learned Updated: 29 April
- cleared the disk space from 66% disk usage on the /root partition, to 54% usage

Next Steps Updated: 29 April
- waiting on confirmation from the customer that all is well now
